Name: Financial Cash Incentives IPH

Caption.String: Inflation does not apply to the PBI amount. In Schedule mode, use nominal (current) dollar values. See Help for details.

Description.String: Type a Federal PBI amount ($/MMBtu) for each year. Use nominal dollars. SAM does not apply inflation to the PBI amount.
Type an Other PBI amount ($/MMBtu) for each year. Use nominal dollars. SAM does not apply inflation to the PBI amount.
Type a State PBI amount ($/MMBtu) for each year. Use nominal dollars. SAM does not apply inflation to the PBI amount.
Type a Utility PBI amount ($/MMBtu) for each year. Use nominal dollars. SAM does not apply inflation to the PBI amount.
